striped pajamas.

496
00:35:15,600 --> 00:35:21,800
- Looked like another tigger to me.
- Oh, no, it's not. I'm the only tigger.

497
00:35:21,800 --> 00:35:25,200
Watch me scare the stripes
off of this impostor.

498
00:35:30,200 --> 00:35:32,700
