Rain, rain, rain
came down, down, down

595
00:43:04,800 --> 00:43:07,000
When the rain, rain, rain
came down, down, down

596
00:43:07,100 --> 00:43:11,500
So the Hundred-Acre Wood
got floodier and floodier.

597
00:43:11,600 --> 00:43:14,500
But the water couldn't come up
