there's a great deal of bouncing.

690
00:49:03,000 --> 00:49:05,900
There is? Oh.

691
00:49:06,000 --> 00:49:08,100
I think that I just remembered...

692
00:49:08,200 --> 00:49:10,300
something that
I forgot to do yesterday...

693
00:49:10,400 --> 00:49:13,100
